**How do I identify team members in the community?**

 @Avitus Core
 The core builders of Avitus, handling the tech, VMs, and all processes to scale Avitus to new heights.

@Avitus Team 
This role is held by the marketing geniuses at Avitus, responsible for marketing and community initiatives.

@Avitus Warden
 This role is held by our dedicated community caretakers and core team contributors.

**🚧 Invite Role’s 🚧**

Invite your friends to join the Avitus journey and unlock these exclusive roles—perfect for advancing in Galxe Quests!

@3 Invites Invite three members to our discord and get recognized.

@5 Invites Invite five members to our discord and get recognized.

@10 Invites Invites Invite ten members to our discord and get recognized.
